title.en: Zetsumetsukigushu Hanayome Shiitagerareta Hime desu ga Ouji-sama no Noroi wo Hodoite Shiawase ni narimasu
Kore kara Shiawase ni narimasu! Shiitagerare Reijou desu ga Tekitaikoku no Koushaku-sama ni Naze ka Dekiaisaretemasu
Shinigami Koushaku no Yatoware Tsuma ni narimashita ga, Kodomo-tachi ga Kawai sugite Mainichi Shiawase desu!
Prince Ryou no Ouji-sama - 7-nin no Bara Monogatari
Tsukareta Ouji-sama to Kyouikugakari no Goreijou no Hanashi
Hakushaku Reijou ni Natte Ojou-sama no Kekkon wo Buchikowashimasu!
Denka, Rien Zentei no Kekkon Seikatsu, Ika ga desu ka?
Jimi de Nekura na Watashi desu ga, Naze ka Ikemen-gaka kara Koibito Yaku wo Tanomarete Konwaku shiteimasu
Shi ni Modori no Sachiusu Reijou, Konse de wa Saikyou Last Boss Ogikei-sama ni Dekiaisaretemasu
Shiitagerareta Hanayome wa Reitetsu Ryou-sama ni Dekiaisareru
Kimi wo Shitte Hana ni naru
Koi wo Shiranai Majo Minarai wa Wakeari Ouji to Mahou Mitai na Koi wo suru
Botsuraku Reijou na no ni Dai 2 Ouji ni Kyuukonsaretemasu
"Jimide Tsumaranai" to Suterareta no de, Jimichi ni Renkinjutsushi wo Mezashimasu!
Nariyuki de Konyaku wo Moushikonda Yowaki Binbou Reijou desuga, Nazeka Jiki Koushaku-sama ni Dekiai sarete Torawarete imasu
Usagi wa Shiawase na Yume wo Miru
